      "originalText": "Key idea:\n\nThe AI reads these files to understand\nthe project's rules and patterns.\n\nIt follows the same conventions a human\ndeveloper would \u2014 consistent code style,\narchitecture, and testing standards.\n\nWhen we integrate the existing site, we'll\ncreate new change proposals here.",
